<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>We can confirm that 1 of the referrals you made has not been successful.&nbsp;</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Due to the Data Protection Act, we are unable to supply any details relating to another customer. However, we have added below some common scenarios that can lead to a referral being unsuccessful.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Why has my referral been unsuccessful?</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Here are some of the common reasons, why a referral may be unsuccessful:</font></div><div style=""><ul><li><font face="arial">They chose not to join our RAF scheme</font></li><li><font face="arial">They chose not to get a quote from Kingsbridge&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="arial">They already had a quote open with Kingsbridge prior to your referral</font></li><li><font face="arial">They chose not to purchase an insurance policy from Kingsbridge</font></li><li><font face="arial">They already held a policy with Kingsbridge</font></li><li><font face="arial">They opted to cancel their Kingsbridge insurance policy during their legal cooling off period</font></li></ul></div><div style=""><font face="arial">You may be able to get more information by speaking with the person you referred. We are happy to speak with them directly to explain the circumstances if required.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>